Subject: Needs help deleting things
Description:
Received this email from the end user. "s there an email or phone number for support?  I tried to open a ticket but it’s not working and I don’t have the time or patience for it.
Just need to delete some things and want to find out if you guys have an API."
Tried to call but didn't get a response.
Solution_Comment__c:
We have cleared some pace in the backend. You should be now at around 52% disk space occupied from 80%.

In order to prevent this please try:
- using the Audit Log Backup functionality -> it will archive the logs and remove them from the EPP server(you can apply this to old logs).
- this functionality can be enabled from System Maintenance -> Audit Log Backup
